r)/ r!</span></p><p dir=3D"ltr"><b><strong>=E2=87=92 C(n,r) =3D n!/(n=E2=88=
=92r)!r!</strong></b></p></blockquote><p dir=3D"ltr"><span>Thus, the formul=
